  "datasetVersion": {
    "title": "NeuroKit2: The Python Toolbox for Neurophysiological Signal Processing",
    "description": "<p>NeuroKit2 is a user-friendly, accessible Python toolbox for neurophysiological signal processing. It provides a comprehensive suite of tools for processing signals from various modalities, including electrocardiography (ECG), electrodermal activity (EDA), electromyography (EMG), photoplethysmography (PPG), electroencephalography (EEG), and more.</p>",
